## TypeScript Rules

- No `any` types. Use `unknown` and narrow, or define proper types in `/lib/types`.
- All Supabase table row types live in `/lib/types/database.ts`.
- All API request/response shapes are typed in `/lib/types/api.ts`.
- Use `zod` for runtime validation on all API route inputs.

