## Do Not Do

- Do not write custom input, button, card, or modal components — use shadcn
- Do not call Gemini API from client components
- Do not use `any` in TypeScript
- Do not hardcode color hex values in components — use Tailwind tokens
- Do not use `next/router` — use `next/navigation`
- Do not fetch Supabase with the service role key on the client
- Do not hardcode prompt strings in API routes — put them in `/lib/prompts`
- Do not use `<a>` tags for internal navigation — use Next.js `<Link>`
